org.cloudgraph.state.State

  • Packages that use State 
    Package Description
    org.cloudgraph.hbase.io
    Provides infrastructure for managing HBase read and write operations across any number of HBase tables and/or rows.
    org.cloudgraph.state
    Contains classes used to manages a minimal set of "state" information persisted with each data graph in order to reduce overall storage space.
